            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Not usually. Most modern architectures use both — a "lakehouse" pattern where the lake stores raw data and a warehouse (or warehouse-like layer) serves the cleaned analytical models used by BI tools.</p></div></div>
          </div>
